column4: Never place the welding helmet on heat surface
Never open or temper with the filter cartridge
Clean the helmet with mild soap and luckwarm water
Do not use welding helmet when
helmet provide protection for intended purpose only
if the lens or front retaining frame is loose
the welding helmet is not suitable for plasma cutting or laser welding
the welding helmet will not protect against explosive devices
Regularly replace the Front Lens Cover if it becomes cracked or scratched or damaged
when servicing use only identical replacement parts
only use accessories intended for use with this helmet
